    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that's ready for its next chapter? This vehicle is a solid performer that gets the job done! While it shows some honest signs of its time on the road\u2014including some cosmetic wear and minor mechanical character\u2014it remains a dependable and practical choice for anyone seeking great value. It's a hardworking car with plenty of life left for its next owner!",
