    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently suffers from significant mechanical issues, including a failing transmission and a severe oil leak that requires immediate attention. The exterior has multiple large dents, peeling clear coat, and rust spots, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear on the upholstery. This car is best suited for someone with mechanical skills looking for a major project or for those needing specific parts.",
